===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# A name for a people or a language or a city etc. which is not used by the natives themselves. ''[[German]]s'', for example, is a xenonym for people who call themselves ''[[Deutsche]]'', ''[[Cologne]]'' a xenonym for ''[[Köln]]'', ''[[Austria]]'' for ''[[Österreich]]'' etc.
